Courtney Peters was last seen in Salberau on the corner of Milky Way and Grand View Avenue on Thursday morning. CAPE TOWN - Elsies River police are investigating the disappearance of a three-year-old girl in the area. Courtney Peters was last seen in Salberau on the corner of Milky Way and Grand View Avenue at about 8.00am on Thursday morning.She was reported missing on Thursday night. The little girl was wearing a yellow and white shirt and blue shorts at the time of her disappearance.(Edited by Zamangwane Shange)